<h1>8 best <em>rainy day activities</em> in Pattaya</h1>
<p class="sub">A Pattaya downpour rarely lasts all day, but when it does, you want a plan. These are the eight indoor things to do in Pattaya we actually send people to when the sky opens — aquariums, malls, spas, indoor adventure and more, with real prices and hours.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">TW</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Tom Whitfield</b>
<span>Activities &amp; adventure editor · Chonburi</span>
</div>
