<h1>12 best <em>restaurants with a view</em> in Pattaya</h1>
<p class="sub">Sea, city or sunset — these are the Pattaya restaurants where the table is worth the trip. We ranked 12 of the best restaurants with a view, from Pratumnak clifftops to Jomtien beachfront and Central rooftops, with real prices and the times to book.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Senior writer · 7 years living in Pattaya</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
