<h1>10 best <em>romantic</em> things to do in Pattaya for couples</h1>
<p class="sub">Pattaya isn't all neon and Walking Street. We mapped the genuinely romantic side — sunset dinners, quiet beaches, couples spas and rooftop bars — into 10 dates that actually work, with real 2026 prices.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · 5 years across Chonburi</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 10, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
<button aria-label="Share this article" type="button"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-share"></use></svg></button>
</div>
