<li><a href="#how-we-picked">How we picked these</a></li>
<li><a href="#sunset">1. Chase the sunset on Pratumnak</a></li>
<li><a href="#dinner">2. Dinner with a sea view</a></li>
<li><a href="#spa">3. A couples spa afternoon</a></li>
<li><a href="#koh-larn">4. A slow day on Koh Larn</a></li>
<li><a href="#rooftop">5. Rooftop bars &amp;amp; a nightcap</a></li>
<li><a href="#quiet-beaches">6–10. Quiet beaches, gardens &amp;amp; more</a></li>
<li><a href="#costs">What a romantic day costs</a></li>
