<h1>Sanctuary of Truth vs <em>Nong Nooch</em>: which is worth your day?</h1>
<p class="sub">Two of Pattaya's most-photographed attractions, two very different half-days. We compare the Sanctuary of Truth and Nong Nooch Tropical Garden on cost, time, location and who each suits — with real 2026 ticket prices, not the inflated ones tour desks quote.</p>
