 best cafes with sea views?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Pratumnak has the best elevated, open-horizon views; Jomtien and Na Jomtien have the most relaxed, affordable all-day cafes and the only true on-the-sand tables; and Naklua's Wong Amat beach is the calmest with the best sunsets. Choose Pratumnak for the photo, Jomtien for the hang, Naklua for the quiet."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Are sea view cafes in Pattaya good for working or laptops?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Jomtien's beachfront cafes are the best for working — relaxed, affordable, with easy parking and space to settle in for a couple of hours. Most have wifi, though check the seaward shaded tables for power. Go in the morning when it's quiet; the brunch crowd arrives after 1pm."}}]}]$b$);
