<h1>Best <em>Seafood</em> in Pattaya: 8 Spots That Aren't Tourist Traps</h1>
<p class="sub">Skip Beach Road. Real Pattaya seafood is in Jomtien, Naklua and the unnamed Bali Hai stalls — chosen by an editor who lives here and orders three times a week, with honest prices and how not to get scammed.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Senior writer · 7 years in Pattaya</span>
</div>
