<div class="compare-foot">Go To Pattaya same-day price audit, March 18, 2026. Beach Road sample: an anonymous restaurant between Soi 7 and Soi 8. Jomtien sample: Mae Sri Ruen Seafood. All dishes ordered identically.</div>
