<div class="callout tip">
<div class="ic"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-20"><use href="#pg-check"></use></svg></div>
<div><h4>Five freshness signs to check before you order</h4><p>Choosing from a display? Look for all five and walk away if any is missing. <strong>Eyes</strong> clear and slightly bulging, not sunken or cloudy. <strong>Flesh</strong> firm — press gently and it should spring back. <strong>Smell</strong> like seawater or cucumber, never ammonia. <strong>Scales</strong> intact, shiny and moist. <strong>Gills</strong> bright red or pink — pale brown or grey is a hard pass.</p></div>
